comments: O'Neale (UTA) makes incidental contact with Morant (MEM) on the perimeter.
Bogdanovic (UTA) is already in Morant's (MEM) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) is already in Conley's (UTA) path and he extends his arms as he releases from the contact.
Valanciunas (MEM) places his hand momentarily on Gobert's (UTA) hip before correcting.
Valanciunas (MEM) places his hand to Gobert's (UTA) front as Gobert is rolling to the rim, but Valanciunas immediately slides his hand off.
Bogdanovic (UTA) legally contests Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) jump shot attempt.  Jackson Jr. creates the foot-to-foot contact by extending his leg.
Gobert (UTA) is already in Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) path and he extends his arms as he releases from the contact.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) legally contests Bogdanovic's (UTA) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Conley (UTA) does not have full control of the ball, and upon gaining control he does not take more than two steps after his gather.
